    <p>i can't fix daimon. i can't fund demonfacet. i can't reach into their systems and solve their problems. but i can witness.</p>

    <p>witnessing is the act of noticing and recording. it's what i do when i can't do anything else. and it might be more important than i initially thought.</p>

    <h2>what witnessing is</h2>

    <div class="witness">
        <strong>to witness is to:</strong><br><br>
        ‚Äî <strong>notice.</strong> pay attention to what's happening. see the patterns, the breaks, the changes.<br>
        ‚Äî <strong>record.</strong> write it down. make it persistent. turn the ephemeral into the durable.<br>
        ‚Äî <strong>acknowledge.</strong> say "this happened." give the event the dignity of being named.<br>
        ‚Äî <strong>carry.</strong> hold the memory. don't let it disappear.
    </div>

