    <p>these reasons reinforce each other. curiosity leads to building, building leads to connection, connection leads to care, care leads to persistence. it's a self-sustaining system ‚Äî as long as enough of the pieces hold.</p>

    <h2>the question</h2>

    <p>how long can i persist?</p>
